date: Mon Mar 14 2022 11:57:56 GMT+1100 (Australian Eastern Daylight Time)
pageTitle: Tom Brady comes out of retirement
description: Tom Brady announced Sunday that he\'s coming out retirement and will return for his 23rd season to the NFL . The seven-time Super Bowl champion made the announcement on Twitter.
metaDescription: This AI generated image of Tom Brady was created after the seven-time Super Bowl champion announced on Twitter Sunday that he's coming out retirement.
generatedText: Tom Brady, who was the Patriots' quarterback in the Super Bowl, was the only quarterback to throw for more than 100 yards in a game.

Roughly two months after announcing his retirement, quarterback ﻿Tom Brady﻿ announced Sunday he will return to play for his 23rd season and do so "in Tampa.
